      <ul class="list-clean">
        <li><strong>00:00 — The framing.</strong> Why this project exists, who it's for.</li>
        <li><strong>02:30 — The survey, briefly.</strong> The three numbers and what they imply.</li>
        <li><strong>06:00 — Maria's twin.</strong> The simulator scenario, narrated.</li>
        <li><strong>11:30 — Cost, ROI, privacy.</strong> The barriers — addressed, not dismissed.</li>
        <li><strong>17:00 — One thing to take away.</strong> If you remember nothing else.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

