        <h3>The podcast works if…</h3>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Listen-through:</strong> ≥40% median completion rate on platform analytics.</li>
          <li><strong>Reach:</strong> ≥50 unique plays across platforms within 14 days of publish.</li>
          <li><strong>Engagement:</strong> ≥3 substantive comments or DMs from Ontario marketing professionals.</li>
          <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> transcript published within 48h of episode release.</li>
